channel.title: Telport for new home HELP!
channel.description: Hey guys, So i made a new home for my server and i made the command ::home for the new home. but when i click the home icon in the quest tab it sends me to the old home! how do i fix this? and where do i go to fix it. Thanks guys.

item.title: Telport for new home HELP!
item.dc:creator: @ezzi ezzi
item.description:
@ezzi wrote:

Go to clickbuttons.java, and look for something like case 4171: or something, and it says
c.getPA().startTeleport(###, ###, 0, “modern”);
Just change the ####
Not sure on the case 4171 btw it’s similar to that though just search your old homes coordinates

When you click an icon an interface or something, like that spell, an action is executed, those are called action buttons, so as somones has said It should be in ActionSender, clickingbuttons, actionbuttons, or some file that HAS to do with action or buttons.
